THIS PROJECT HAS MOVED TO SOURCEHUT!: https://sr.ht/~nickbp/gridmgr/

I'm consolidating my personal projects in one place. As such the old GitHub repo is being archived, and work now continues on sourcehut.

===

Building gridmgr:

1) Install libx11-dev, and optionally libxinerama-dev
2) "mkdir bin; cd bin"
3) "cmake ../src"
4) "make"
5) See "bin/gridmgr"

Docs: http://nickbp.github.io/gridmgr/
